			    from {top: 0;}

			@keyframes _aimtellShake {

			  }

			pushboxcontainer{
			    position:fixed;
			    z-index:1000201;
			    top:15px;
			    left:60px;
			    font-family:times;
			    display: block;
			    -webkit-animation: _aimtellShowPushBox 1s forwards;
			    animation: _aimtellShowPushBox 1s forwards;

			}
			pushbox {
			    position: relative;
			    background: #FFF;
			    -webkit-border-radius: 10px;
			    -moz-border-radius: 10px;
			    border-radius: 10px; 
			    width: 325px; 
			    padding: 10px;
			    padding-top:15px;
			    display:block;
			    border:1px solid #E9E9E9;
			    box-shadow: 0 15px 45px -5px rgba(39,55,74,.15), 0 15px 40px -20px rgba(39, 55, 74, 0.35);
			    font-size:16px;
			    line-height:20px;
			    letter-spacing:normal;
			    text-transform: initial;
			}

			pushbox:before{
			    content: '';
			    position: absolute;
			    top: -25px;
			    left:25px;
			    z-index: 1;
			    border: solid 15px transparent;
			    border-bottom-color: #f3f3f3;
			}

			pushbox:after {
			    content: '';
			    position: absolute;
			    top: -24px;
			    left:25px;
			    z-index: 1;
			    border: solid 15px transparent;
			    border-bottom-color: #FFF;
			}

			pushbox noticon{
			    width:15%;
			    float:left;
			    display: block;
			    margin:0 auto;
			    margin-top:5px;
			    text-align: center;
			}

			pushbox noticon:hover{
				 animation: _aimtellShake 0.82s linear both;
				 cursor:pointer;
			}

			pushbox:hover noticon{
				 animation: _aimtellShake 0.82s linear both;
			}

			pushbox notibody{
			    width:75%;
			    float:left;
			    text-align:left;
			    font-size:16px;
			    padding-left:10px;
			}

			pushbox noticlose{
			    position:absolute;
			    right:15px;
			    top:15px;
			    color:#C9C9C9;
			    cursor: pointer;
			    z-index:1000201;
			}

			pushbox pushbox-cta buttons{
			  position:relative;
			  display:inline-block;
			  clear:both;
			  width:100%;
			  font-size:16px;
			}

			pushbox pushbox-cta buttons button-approve, pushbox pushbox-cta buttons button-deny{
			    display:inline-block; 
			    margin-top:10px;
			    float:right;
			    margin-right:10px;
			    min-width: 75px
			}

			pushbox teaser{
			    font-weight:700;
			    font-size:17px;
			    color: #000000;
			}

			pushbox teaser, pushbox teaser-byline{
			  display:block;
			  position:relative;
			}

			pushbox teaser-byline{
			    color: #000000;
			}

			pushbox button-approve,pushbox button-deny{
			  cursor: pointer;
			  transition: all 60ms ease-in-out;
			  text-align: center;
			  white-space: nowrap;
			  color: #fff;
			  border: 0 none;
			  border-radius: 4px;
			  padding:5px 10px;
			}

			pushbox img._aimtellBell{
			  margin:0 auto;
			  cursor:pointer;
			}

			pushbox noticon svg{
				width:30px;
				height:30px;
			}

			pushbox powered{
				display:none;
			}

			pushbox powered{
			  font-size:12px;
			  width:100%;
			  display:block;
			  margin-top:10px;
			  padding:5px 0px;
			  padding-right:10px;
			  text-align:right;
			  border-top:1px solid #C9C9C9;
			  display:none;
			}

			pushbox ._aimtellPromptApprove{
			  background-color: #ffffff;
			  color:#0368ff;
			}
			
			pushbox ._aimtellPromptDeny{
			  background-color: #ffffff;
			  color:#919191;
			}
